      <description>&lt;p&gt;The research training group &lt;em&gt;MathCoRe&lt;/em&gt; at that OVGU provides a both challenging and supporting environment for a small community of graduate students to pursue a PhD in a field that relates to mathematical complexity reduction.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Currently, I&amp;rsquo;m supervising two PhD students in this project and there is always a chance to set up another PhD project &amp;ndash; please use the above link to see the scope of &lt;em&gt;MathCoRe&lt;/em&gt; and just apply.&lt;/p&gt;
